        <abstract> 
<p>Writes to correct a statement made in his 1837 paper "On the formation of mould" [<hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 1: 49–53]. He should have said that marl was put on the field 30 years ago, not 80. Observations made on a visit to the field showed that worms had undermined the marl spread on the field at a faster rate than previously reported.</p> 
        </abstract>
